messages.subject: when mathematicians model
messages.msgSnippet: A female friend of mine has told people (men and women both) that she s a statistician who does mathematical modelling, and some of them have looked at her
messages.messageBody:
A female friend of mine has told people (men and women both) that she's a
statistician who does mathematical modelling, and some of them have looked at
her with the twinkie eyes they used to draw in Mad magazine and said, "Oh,
you're a model?"

I guess when she's saying "statistician and mathematical" their brains just
shut down.

Sandra
